# Privacy Policy


## Introduction
Welcome to Nusqa ("we", "our", "us"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. 
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application (the "Nusqa").

##Information We Collect
We do not collect, use, or share any personal data from users of our App.
Your privacy is our top priority, and we have designed our App to function without requiring access to your personal information.

##Permissions We Request
For the App to function correctly, we request the following permissions:

###Internet Access:
Required to access the internet for app functionality.

###Phone Call:
We use this permission to enable users to initiate phone calls via URLs directly from the app. 
This action is user-initiated, and we do not collect or store any information related to your calls.

###WhatsApp:
We use this permission to enable users to initiate WhatsApp conversations via URLs directly from the app.
This action is user-initiated, and we do not collect or store any information related to your WhatsApp usage.

###Share Feature:
Allows users to share the app or content via other applications installed on their device.
This action is user-initiated, and we do not collect or store any information related to what or how you share.

##Use of Your Information
As we do not collect or use any personal data, there are no details to provide regarding the usage of information.

##Health Claims and Remedies
The health-related information and remedies provided in our App are based on scientifically proven evidence from Unani and Ayurveda practices.
These remedies have been supported by research published in official scientific papers. However, this information is not intended as medical advice.
Always consult with a qualified healthcare professional before starting any new treatment or regimen.

##Testimonials Disclaimer
The testimonials provided within the App are the individual experiences and opinions of those who have used our product. These testimonials are not intended to represent or guarantee that anyone will achieve the same or similar results. We do not claim that the testimonials are typical results that users will generally achieve. Your experience may vary.

##Sources Disclaimer
The sources referenced in this app are from reputable and authentic scientific research and official publications.
While we strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information, we recommend that users verify the information with additional sources and consult with a qualified healthcare professional before applying any health-related information or remedies mentioned in this app.
Nusqa is not responsible for any errors or omissions in the content provided, nor for any outcomes related to the use of this information. Always seek professional advice for specific medical conditions or concerns.

##No Endorsement
The inclusion of testimonials and health-related information in our app does not constitute an endorsement or recommendation by us.
We do not claim that our products or services will provide specific benefits or that our customers will achieve the same results.

##Consultation Services
Nusqa provides free consultation services within the app. These services are conducted by qualified professionals.
However, the information provided during the consultation is for general informational purposes only and should not be considered medical advice.
Always consult with a healthcare provider for medical advice specific to your situation.

###Data Collection 
We do not collect any personal information during the consultation process unless explicitly provided by the user for the purpose of the consultation.
Any information shared during the consultation is kept confidential and is not shared with third parties.
###User Consent
Before starting a consultation, users must provide explicit consent acknowledging that they understand and agree to the terms of the consultation disclaimer and this privacy policy.

##Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy,
please contact us at nusqaservices@gmail.com.
